

= a platform for modern polemics in the field of internet governance

URL = http://en.collaboratory.de/w/Discussion_Paper_Series

=Description=

"MIND stands for Multistakeholder Internet Dialogue. The discussion paper series is a platform for modern polemics in the field of internet governance. Each issue is structured around a central argument in form of a proposition of a well-known author, which is then commented by several actors from academia and the technical communities, the private sector, as well as civil society and government in form of replications."


